and doing more
with the money, is

00:39:27.640 --> 00:39:30.590
immensely helpful to the
future, health and wealth,

00:39:30.590 --> 00:39:33.050
as Vint put it, of America.

00:39:33.050 --> 00:39:34.090
KIM: Thanks, Gary.

