00:50:57.330 --> 00:51:00.830
We'd been going after
the Clinton Foundation.

00:51:00.830 --> 00:51:02.997
And we were getting pushed
back, pushed back, pushed

00:51:02.997 --> 00:51:03.496
Back.

00:51:03.496 --> 00:51:05.515
This past January, I was
with President Clinton,

00:51:05.515 --> 00:51:07.732
